quran[8{c,v,t}:
2,30,aur ( woh waqt yaad karne ke qabil hai ) jab tumahray perwar-digaar ne firshton se farmaya ke mein zameen mein ( apna ) naib bananay wala hon. unhon ne kaha.kiya too is mein aisay shakhs ko naib banana chahta hai jo kharabian kere aur kasht wa khoon karta phiray aur hum teri tareef ke sath tasbeeh wa taqdees karte rehtay hain. ( khuda ne ) farmaya mein woh baatein jaanta hon jo tum nahi jantay
2,31,aur is ne aadam ko sab ( cheezon ke ) naam sikhayiye phir un ko firshton ke samnaykiya aur farmaya ke agar tum sachey ho to mujhe un ke naam batao
2,32,"unhon ne kaha, to pak hai. jitna ilm to ne hamein bakhsha hai, is ke siwa hamein kuch maloom nahi. be shak to Dana ( aur ) hikmat wala hai"
2,33,( tab ) khuda ne ( aadam ko ) hukum diya ke aadam! tum un ko un ( cheezon ) ke naam batao. jab unhon ne un ko un ke naam betaye to ( firshton se ) farmaya kyun mein ne tum se nahi kaha tha ke mein asmano aur zameen ki ( sab ) posheeda baatein janta hon aur jo tum zahir karte ho aur jo posheeda karte ho ( sab ) mujh ko maloom hai
2,34,aur jab hum ne firshton ko hukum diya ke aadam ke agay sajda karo to woh sjday mein gir parre magar shetan ne inkaarkiya aur ghuroor mein aakar kafir ban gaya
2,35,aur hum ne kaha ke ae aadam tum aur tumhari biwi bahisht mein raho aur jahan se chaho be rok toak khao ( piyo ) lekin is darakht ke paas nah jana nahi to zaalmon mein ( daakhil ) ho jao ge
2,36,"phir shetan ne dono ko wahan se phsla diya aur jis ( aish wa nishaat ) mein they, is se un ko nikalwa diya. tab hum ne hukum diya ke ( bahisht bareen se ) chalay jao. tum aik dosray ke dushman ho, aur tumahray liye zameen mein aik waqt taq thikana aur muaash ( muqarrar kar diya gaya ) hai"
2,37,phir aadam ne apne perwar-digaar se kuch kalmaat sekhe ( aur maffi mangi ) to is ne un ka qasoor maaf kar diya be shak woh maaf karne wala ( aur ) sahib reham hai
